data.description: Welcome to this stunning one-story, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence nestled in a serene community, embraced by the beauty of nature and conveniently located just minutes from town. Step into a bright and open-concept home adorned with delightful wood accents. The updated kitchen boasts elegant countertops, offering a warm welcome. A bonus room is at your disposal for creative projects or accommodating visiting family and friends. Embrace outdoor living with a covered patio for entertaining and a spacious backyard for play. Your feathered friends will feel at home in the ready-to-go chicken coop, while the shed provides additional garden storage. Discover your future abode, complete with a brand-new septic and leach field system, and make it your own!
